{
  "stem": "182.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 171.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got to a town named [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's a small village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the man who  was taking us with his wagon, he didn't want to go any further because he was attracting attention.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was afraid that the German-- the Germans will catch him, that he's transporting a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they put us down in this down, and we didn't know how to go any further.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the man came from Kolomaya for provisions-- a Jew, with a truck, with a German truck.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we talked to this man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I always say that he was our angel sent from God.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he took us to Kolomaya on the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when we were in this building of the Judenrat where there were other people who came from the villages and they had nowheres to be, then he always came to see how we are doing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he came, and he said that they're going to close the doors of the ghetto, and there will be no way to get out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had some bread and some potatoes, some beans that we took with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he took that and sold it, and he paid for a German car, a driver.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we sat in this car, and it was wonderful to see how all the gates opened in front of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we came again to the Dniester.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they came to the Dniester, and by then the Dniester was frozen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because this was before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we crossed on foot, the Dniester, and we came to a Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we slept in a chair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the next day, we still had a  little money left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We hired a wagon who took us back to Jagielnica.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then this doctor saw us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
